  <brief_title>Local Infiltration Analgesia With Ropivacaine in Posterior Vaginal Wall Prolapse:a Randomized, Double-Blind Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Lokal Infiltrations Analgesi Med Ropivakain 1 % Versus Placebo VED Vaginale Descensusoperationer: ET Prospektivt Randomiseret, Dobbeltblindet, Placebo- Kontrolleret Studie</official_title>
  <sponsors>
